title: DIR EN GREY - 5 Ugly Kingdom - Live - DVDRip * 2003 *
description:
[b]Rettou Gekishin Angya Final 2003 5 Ugly Kingdom[/b] is a live DVD and VHS released by Dir en grey on May 21, 2003. The featured concert was performed at the Yokohama Arena, as the last show of the year-long Rettou Gekishin Angya tour. This was the band&#039;s first live release to make use of a 16:9 aspect ratio and DTS audio (DVD only).
